What can you expect?

1. Ability to upload files locally.
2. Ability to upload files to RackspaceCloud and other Cloud services.
3. Retrieve files from the cloud.
4. Ability resize images and store the different sizes.

Requirements

# Curl - http://www.php.net/manual/en/book.curl.php
# FileInfo - http://www.php.net/manual/en/book.fileinfo.php
# GD - http://www.php.net/manual/en/book.image.php
